{"tid":2433957,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年遇警掃蕩被指逃避追捕遭毆5棍 香淑嫻裁定罪成判監8星期","createTime":"2021-03-05T08:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T15:48:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"58bc4f714b040a35402ad967922a15851b65d457","tid":2433957,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14166&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=32bb5b3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14166</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官 #裁決 #判刑<br />\n👤李(20) #1006旺角 (原案D3)<br />\n <br />\n控罪3：抗拒警務人員 #拒捕<br />\n被控於2019年10月6日，在九龍旺角窩打老道65號地下外，抗拒在執行職責的督察21982。 <br />\n<br />\n審訊索引：<br />\n第一天審訊Part 1 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14106&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=9cff039b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14106</a>)<br />\n第一天審訊Part 2 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14119&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=a343b68f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14119</a>)<br />\n結案陳詞 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14146&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=e1a86e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14146</a>)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n🛑罪名成立.....詳情後補<br />\n<br />\n🛑判刑：<br />\n法庭同意本案情節較輕微，但由於本案發生在暴力示威活動中，有疑犯正在逃跑，法庭認為被告人行為會激發他人情緒，而且上訴庭已就高偉傑案中要求就此類型案件中判處阻嚇性判刑，但考慮到被告沒有案底，故判處被告人8星期監禁。"},{"pid":"288e67a6f93f49774c15ede8c9cf6ce3b4d3e8f7","tid":2433957,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"一名青年被指在前年10月於旺角拒捕，期間無視警員警告，更擺動身體企圖掙脫警員控制，最終警方需以警棍擊打其大腿5下始能制服。<br />\n<br />\n時任西九龍衝鋒隊指揮官譚健燊供稱，當日凌晨零時許，他乘警車在旺角一帶兜截，期間見到一批穿黑衣的人士聚集，他們見警員前來便四散。警車加速追捕，至案發地點對開譚落車，在約5米外見到孭藍色背囊的被告並展開追截，沿途多番說「警察，咪走！」，惟被告沒理會。<br />\n<br />\n譚憶述，他跑約100米後追及被告，用左手捉着對方的右手。此時，被告卻左右擺動身體，試圖大力「揈甩」他。譚再次警告無效後，取出警棍並擊打被告右大腿外側5次，此時被告終放棄抵抗，譚及其同僚合力將被告制服。譚認為，自己作出口頭警告時聲音響亮，現場環境不算嘈雜。"},{"pid":"174dc32481a8090e5b9bdc67d0f655c080fb9838","tid":2433957,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"重撚到"},{"pid":"a1e7a180b76f586f539474806064e47c7302fb70","tid":2433957,"uid":279333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ff6a2c01b23ec9cb1710b5b38f49875e71c514","tid":2433957,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef1d489892a021f99e0a11e210058e05297b8f","tid":2433957,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"辯方詢問警方是否有使用武力指引，譚回應指引可作一個參考，「（警員）受到咩程度反抗，要用咩武力，由警員自己根據情況決定。」辯方詢問譚是否用最低武力處理被告；譚稱「我哋盡量用合理武力，但都有教過如果要達到某啲目的，（使用）高一級武力亦可以。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">辯方又質疑譚在記事冊稱捉住被告之後，他才說「警察咪郁」，與庭上內容不符。譚則表示「time frame 好短，notebook 唔詳細，唔代表冇咁發生</span></strong>，口供係詳細啲。」辯方又指，譚沒有在記事冊寫下同袍跟他一起制服被告；譚反駁在首句已交代有警員跟他一起行動，「睇唔到有必要佢每次要出現（在記事冊）。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\